==Mission-Specific==
===(Trailblazer), I imagine you...===
{{Messages
|start_condition = 
|text =
:'''Black Swan:''' (Trailblazer), I imagine you have already seen that dream bubble?
:'''Black Swan:''' Relax, I just want to know if anyone has come looking for you yet
:{Choice} What happened?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What happened?
:{Choice} I'm getting déjà vu here...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm getting déjà vu here...
:'''Black Swan:''' You may also know that interesting young Fool, Sparkle.
:'''Black Swan:''' She's recently gotten into disguising herself as other people. (Trailblazer), has she tried this with you already?
:{Choice} Wait... Then you might be...
:'''(Trailblazer):''' If that's the case, you could be Sparkle in disguise, too.
:'''Black Swan:''' I see you're on high alert. What would you have me do to prove I am "me"?
:{Choice} A unique expression?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Some unique linguistic habits, like whether you add full-stops or not to messages
:{Choice} A unique action?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Some unique actions you do out of habit, like looking in the mirror a lot
:'''Black Swan:''' But, if that little Miss Fool excels in observation, there is a chance that she could perfectly imitate everything about a person.
:'''Black Swan:''' I think that the only thing that can differentiate someone from another is their "memories." There is no way for an outsider to completely steal or imitate every ounce of a person's memory.
:'''Black Swan:''' It's just like when we met in Penacony, is it not? A strange dreamland surrounding us, a series of strange murders, people with differing dreams, the truth that lies beneath the water's surface...
:'''Black Swan:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 01.png|80px|(Image) &lbrack;Pom-Pom Sticker - Greet&rbrack;]]
:'''Black Swan:''' Do you need me to go on?
:{Choice} That's enough
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I think that's enough
:{Choice} I need more
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I think I need more
:'''Black Swan:''' I can't be the one doing all the talking. By your logic, you should also have to prove that you are not Sparkle, (Trailblazer).
:{Choice} Huh?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Huh?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 08.png|80px|(Image) &lbrack;Pom-Pom Sticker - Shocked&rbrack;]]
:'''Black Swan:''' I'm just joking. As a Memokeeper, I naturally know who the person is on the other side of my screen.
:'''Black Swan:''' Miss Sparkle's pranks are not without their benefits, she is able to make us re-examine what we have seen and think about the appearance and reality of the Dreamscape. This is also the reason that I shared the dream bubble with you.
:'''Black Swan:''' Alright, looks like she hasn't caused any major damage, I will put my mind at ease. Talk to you again soon!
}}
