===I am curious, (Trailblazer)....===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Black Swan:''' I am curious, (Trailblazer). Having traveled to so many places, have you encountered divination before?
:{Choice} I did on the Xianzhou
::'''(Trailblazer):''' The Xianzhou Luofu uses the Matrix of Prescience to make predictions about the future
::'''Black Swan:''' You mean the Divination Commission, right... I have heard tales of them before.
:{Choice} The Stellaron Hunters use it, too.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I think the Stellaron Hunters have this ability, too.
::'''Black Swan:''' You mean that Destiny's Slave... Say no more.
:'''Black Swan:''' Everyone has their own beliefs when it comes to divination methods. If you ask me, I believe you can predict a person's future using only their memories.
:'''Black Swan:''' This method of divination is based on a law of life, that we are constantly living under the influence of our pasts.
:'''Black Swan:''' The deeper the memory is carved into someone's mind, the more complete and original it is, the clearer the trajectory of the destiny that leads from it.
:'''Black Swan:''' Well, would you like to try?
:{Choice} I don't remember lotsa things
:'''(Trailblazer):''' There are lots of things that I do not remember...
:'''Black Swan:''' Yes, you and that March 7th are very special...
:'''Black Swan:''' As neither of you have any memories for me to divine from, why don't you take the lead and use this method to perform a divination using someone else's memories?
:'''Black Swan:''' There is a reason for every word we speak, you must simply just say what is in your heart.
:'''Black Swan:''' I shall describe a memory to you, you can make predictions about the future based on it as you please.
:{Choice} I can do that?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I can do that?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Then I'm going to be bold and make some predictions!
:{Choice} I'm ready!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Then I'm going to be bold and make some predictions!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 08.png|80px]]
:'''Black Swan:''' "A young girl wanders alone, observing the influence that the past has had on the reality of different worlds and recording those fleeting moments that went overlooked."
:'''Black Swan:''' What kind of future do you think the owner of this memory is headed towards?
:{Choice} A bright future.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Being able to roam alone throughout different worlds, she must be a considerably powerful person
::'''(Trailblazer):''' She enjoys observing the lives of others but is still able to leave without causing a disturbance. I imagine she is an attentive and optimistic person
::'''(Trailblazer):''' So, I imagine that she will live happily, no matter what happens
:{Choice} A bland future.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' If she spends the rest of her life as nothing more than an observer from the sidelines, I imagine her life will be very bland
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Perhaps she will continue like this until she reaches the end of her life, before leaving in silence with no one to remember her
:{Choice} An unfortunate future.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' If she continues to wander the cosmos alone like this, she will inevitably encounter a lot of danger
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It is very likely that she will lose her life along this journey one day
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Also, if she spends her entire life as a bystander and observer, I imagine she will be very lonely
:'''Black Swan:''' I'm glad I was able to hear your thoughts. Not bad.
:'''Black Swan:''' Did that give you a sense of the power within memories? It leads to the future and allows us to catch a glimpse of the whole picture... However, keep in mind that the future can also change, never forget that.
:{Choice} Whose memory was that?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' So, who is the owner of this memory? What is her future like?
:'''Black Swan:''' She may be someone you know, she may also just be a passing figure in your life.
:'''Black Swan:''' Ah, another customer for divination. Talk to you again, soon!
:{Choice} You haven't answered my question
:'''(Trailblazer):''' You haven't answered my question!
}}
