===Come to think of...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Black Swan:''' Come to think of it, did you know that memories related to the sense of smell are some of the strongest and most vivid in humans?
:{Choice} Heard that before
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I feel like I've heard that theory before
:{Choice} Never heard that before
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I've never heard that before
:{Choice} Why did you bring that up?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Hm? What made you bring that up all of a sudden?
:'''Black Swan:''' You see, it's just that I used up all the pine incense I use during divination and a perfumer friend gave me a new box. When I lit it, I realized that the aroma seemed very familiar.
:'''Black Swan:''' Reflecting on my memories, I realized that it must be very similar to the essence of the Trailblaze.
:{Choice} Never thought you'd know these
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I never thought you'd know about things like aromatherapy
:'''Black Swan:''' As I said before, memories related to the sense of smell are some of the strongest in humans.
:'''Black Swan:''' So, certain aromas often come with set memories. Even a Memokeeper like myself sometimes enjoys using these kinds of indirect methods to recall those memories.
:'''Black Swan:''' Next time we meet, I shall bring some of the styles I enjoy for you to experience, too.
:{Choice} [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 03.png|80px]]
:'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 03.png|80px]]
}}
